rows.label: tlk70000029_04_msg0001
rows.name:
If I remember rightly, it's been
decades since they gave a knighthood
to someone who wasn't a proper Iiran.

rows.label: tlk70000029_04_msg0002
rows.name:
No offense meant. Of
course, that's mostly
because we've been at peace.

rows.label: tlk70000029_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But still, this is a glorious day!
The new Ornella-sama! I've not felt
this hopeful in a long time.
